# Frontend Tooling & Documentation

Policies: `.ai/policies/frontend-tooling.md`, `.ai/policies/documentation.md`

## Enforced Commands

```bash
npm run lint           # ESLint + eslint-plugin-jsdoc + architectural rules
npm run format:check   # Prettier
npx commitlint         # Conventional Commits (commit-msg hook)
```

Templates: `.ai/templates/frontend-tooling/`. Root config: `commitlint.config.cjs`.

## JSDoc (Documenter Agent)

Required on all exported functions, classes, types, interfaces, RTK endpoints, public hooks.

## Mermaid (Documenter Agent)

Required in `03-documentation.md` and feature READMEs for non-trivial flows (sequence, state, flowchart).

## Prohibited

- Exported symbols without JSDoc
- Non-conventional commit messages
- `git commit --no-verify`
- `eslint-disable` / `prettier-ignore` without ADR

## Pipeline

Documentation stage (`03-documentation.md`) must PASS before QA.
